Package: thop
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Terminal Hopper for Agents
 thop is a CLI tool that enables AI agents to execute commands on remote
 systems via SSH. It provides a shell wrapper architecture with session
 management, automatic reconnection, and context persistence.
 .
 Features:
  - Interactive mode with readline support
  - Proxy mode for AI agent integration
  - SSH session management with ~/.ssh/config support
  - Automatic reconnection with exponential backoff
  - Environment variable persistence across sessions
  - Configurable startup commands per session
